  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Explain how computer hard drives and graphic tablets operate using magnetic induction</item>
<item>Explain how hybrid/electric vehicles and transcranial magnetic stimulation use magnetic induction to their advantage</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
